title: For Sale:  .223 SNIPER, AR15 PROTOTYPE for Government/LE Use
postcontent:
RIFLE IS WORTH $4500, but I will consider reasonable and real offers, please no jokes, or scammers, this is a one of a kind, prototype, and is worth the money.  The Government paid close to $8000 a copy.

This rifle started life as a CAR15, known as the Colt Accurized Rifle, it is an uncommon variant of the popular AR15.  A Government Agency came to me and asked me to develop a specific weapon which could accomplish a specific mission for long distance absolute accuracy, they wanted to use .223.  I did not ask why, because there are better choices, but nevertheless, this is the prototype.  50 of these were built, and are in service.  This is a one of a kind.  The rifle with a qualified shooter and 77 grain match ammo can and will put them in the same hole out to 300 meters, and within a 1-2 inch group out to 500 meters, with the maximum design range of 700 meters. It is capable to 1000 meters, but has not been tested at that range as that was outside the design parameters of the order.  Note, this is not a manufactured rifle, it is an enhanced original product, so no stamps are required. 

NONE OF THESE ARE IN CIVILIAN HANDS THAT I KNOW OF.  YOU WILL HAVE THE ONLY ONE OUTSIDE OF GOVT OR LE AND ITS PERFECTLY LEGAL TO OWN IT.

The rifle was completely disassembled.  Added was a 23.5" stainless barrel with M4 feed ramps, and threaded for a suppressor and provided with a thread protector.  Barrel is 1:7 twist and is free floated with a solid hand guard, flush gas block.  BCG was printed, and lightened for faster dwell time, bolt was trued.  Trigger was replaced with a skeletonized Timney which was hand polished and set to a crisp 3 pound pull with crisp break and no creep.  Butt stock is the PRS dual adjustable as to cheek piece and length of pull and is equipped with an Accu-pod.  Weapon will arrive with 2 ea, 20 round magazines.  The lower receiver is equipped with a mag carrier for a second loaded mag. 
Scope is a Carl Zeiss 6.5 - 22 X 50 BDC scope for the 77 grain projectile with ranging reticle.  There is an anti cant level on the scope, butler creek flip up optic covers.  Triple screw tactical rings on the Colt base. 

Rifle will be delivered with a custom scope and muzzle cover, a custom fitted blackhawk case, and 50 rounds of match ammunition, 2 ea. 20 round magazines. A Harris tactical bipod with cant lock.   All original and replaced parts will be provided to the buyer and all documentation.  This is the most accurate semi-automatic sniper system (SASS) rifle you will ever handle.  We tested 12 different barrels before deciding on the one installed. Nothing is more perfect. 

This is heavy, and bulky, shipping and packing  CONUS $100.00.  

A zip file of detailed photos is available TO SERIOUS BUYERS ONLY.  Send email.
